        <p class="term-line"><span class="prompt">james@aws:~$</span> ls ~/projects</p>
        <p class="term-out"><a href="/projects/">cloud-site/</a> — this website: S3, CloudFront, Lambda, all Terraform</p>
        <p class="term-out"><a href="/projects/">football-analysis/</a> — Premier League data, scraped and visualised in Python</p>
        <p class="term-out"><a href="/projects/">rust-chip8/</a> — a Chip-8 emulator, built to learn Rust</p>

        <p class="term-line"><span class="prompt">james@aws:~$</span> cat blog/latest.md</p>
        <p class="term-out"><a href="{{ latestPost.url }}">{{ latestPost.data.title }}</a> · {{ latestPost.date | dateReadable }}</p>

        <p class="term-line"><span class="prompt">james@aws:~$</span> curl james-hodson.com/count</p>
        <p class="term-out"><span id="visitor-count">...</span> visitors and counting</p>

        <p class="term-line"><span class="prompt">james@aws:~$</span> <span class="cursor"></span></p>
